                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9071" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2275</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1340 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">做数字经济的“赶潮人”：龙江交投的财务数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Keeping up with digitalization trends Financial Digital Transformation of Heilongjiang Provincial Transportation Investment Group.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">于丽艳，温欣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑龙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑龙江省交通投资集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务数字化转型；数字经济；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">digital transformation; digital economy; micro-cases</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字化转型浪潮的推动下，各行各业纷纷搭乘数字化“快车”，积极探索和革新经营管理模式。交通行业作为国家经济和社会发展的基石，肩负着国计民生的重大使命，对于推动交通强国建设以及国家供给侧结构改革具有举足轻重的地位。随着信息技术的迅猛发展，财务管理面临着前所未有的变革。黑龙江省交通投资集团是黑龙江省内七大投资集团之一，紧跟时代潮流，致力于推动传统综合交通产业的财务数字化转型，以“数字交投”为核心，搭建统一主数据平台，助力业务与财务融合、催生财务共享服务模式建立，进而实现企业财务数字化转型。作为黑龙江省交通投资领域的领军企业，该集团的财务数字化转型实践不仅具有鲜明的代表性，同时也为其他企业提供了宝贵的借鉴经验。
本案例以黑龙江省交通投资集团为案例对象，描述该集团如何进行财务数字化转型。通过本案例的学习，旨在帮助其他企业探索财务数字化转型的有效路径，使学生深入理解财务数字化转型的动因；同时，通过具体案例分析，使学生熟悉数字化转型在企业中的应用过程，启发学生深入思考适用于其他企业财务数字化转型的关键路径和方法，为未来的实践提供有力指导。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the wave of digital transformation, various industries have carried out digital transformation and actively explored new modes of operation and management. The transportation industry, as a key infrastructure related to national economy and people&#39;s livelihood, plays a pivotal role in promoting the construction of a strong transportation country. With the rapid development of information technology, financial management is facing unprecedented changes. Heilongjiang Provincial Transportation Investment Group, one of the seven major investment groups in Heilongjiang Province, follows the trend of the times and is committed to promoting the financial digital transformation of the traditional comprehensive transportation industry, taking “Digital Transportation and Investment” as the core, building a unified master data platform, facilitating the fusion of business and finance, and generating the establishment of a financial shared service model to realize the corporate finance digital transformation. Digital transformation. As a leading enterprise in the field of transportation investment in Heilongjiang Province, the Group&#39;s financial digital transformation practice is not only representative, but also provides valuable experience for other enterprises.
This case takes Heilongjiang Provincial Transportation Investment Group as the case object to describe how the group carries out financial digital transformation. Through the study of this case, we aim to help other enterprises explore the effective path of financial digital transformation, so that students have a deep understanding of the connotation of financial digital transformation and the driving force behind it; at the same time, through the specific case study, we familiarize students with the application process of digital transformation in the enterprise, and inspire students to think deeply about the key paths and methods that are applicable to the digital transformation of the finances of other enterprises, so as to provide powerful guidance for the practice in the future. The course will provide students with powerful guidance for future practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《战略管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型的动因；数字化转型的路径；数字化转型的启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
